title: Deli Jasmin - Llama de Fuego
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Western, Juice bar, Take-out, Guatemalan, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Small place decorated with plants. Small healthy menu, with most breakfast options that use eggs can be served with scrambled tofu instead. Also salads with sprouting seeds, a couple of main courses with option of tofu or tempeh, has brown rice, fresh juices, and smoothies. No smoking.
